      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1) with documented V&V test suite; user-defined hemolysis scalar UDF subject to unit-test suite with 12 canonical cases.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1 carries ISO 9001 quality management certification and FDA-recognized software validation documentation. The in-house power-law hemolysis UDF was validated against three published analytical solutions and nine benchmark transport cases. All 12 unit tests passed within specified tolerances. SQA level 2 achieved."
